name: RuviMix
description:
🍪 RuviMix 🍪

- is a smooth anime art style with colored line-art.

  • Great at making upper body portraits.

  • Great at creating semi-realistic landscapes.

  • Decent with hands. (provided that EasyNegative is in the negatives)

  • Smooth and defined line art.

What's new?

Brighter colors, colored line-art, better response to colored lighting compared to the first version.


✅ Recommended Parameters ✅
Sampler: Euler a: 20 steps.
CFG Scale: 5-7
Hires.fix: Latent (nearest), 20 steps, 0.45 denoising OR, R-Esrgan anime6b, 0.35 denoising
Clip Skip: 2
Negatives: (EasyNegative:1.2), artist name, signature, watermark, logo

Want to generate AI art for free?

My models are available on:

🌟 Yodayo

⚫ TensorArt

💜 PixAi

All of my stuff will be free to use! Support me on Kofi~ ☕
